<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Track your dividend income by month and analyze yield trends">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0e14">
    <title>My Dividend Tracker</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="images/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        :root {
            --bg: #0a0e14;
            --surface: #111621;
            --surface-alt: #161d2b;
            --border: #1e2840;
            --green: #34d399;
            --green-dim: #1a4a35;
            --green-glow: rgba(52,211,153,0.15);
            --text: #e2e8f0;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --text-dim: #475569;
            --red: #f87171;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* ─── NAV ─── */
        nav {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 50;
            background: #0d1117; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 16px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 56px;
        }

        .nav-brand {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
        }

        .nav-brand img {
            height: 28px; width: 28px;
        }

        .nav-brand span {
            color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;
        }

        .nav-buttons {
            display: flex; gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-nav {
            background: var(--surface-alt); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 7px; color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer;
            padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.15s; font-family: inherit;
        }

        .btn-nav:hover {
            background: var(--border); color: var(--text);
        }

        /* ─── MAIN ─── */
        .main {
            padding: 72px 16px 48px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ─── CARDS ─── */
        .cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .card-value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
            color: var(--green);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .card-sub {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ─── SECTION ─── */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .placeholder-box {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px dashed var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .placeholder-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .placeholder-box code {
            display: block;
            background: var(--surface-alt);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 12px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 48px 24px;
        }

        .empty-state-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .empty-state h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .empty-state p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
        <div class="nav-brand">
            <img src="images/app-icon.png" alt="Dividend Tracker">
            <span>My Dividend Tracker</span>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-buttons">
            <button class="btn-nav" onclick="window.location.href='tracker.html'">← Back</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- MAIN -->
<div class="main">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>📊 My Dividend Tracker</h1>
        <p>Track your monthly dividend income and analyze yield trends</p>
    </div>

    <!-- STATS CARDS -->
    <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">2026 YTD</div>
            <div class="card-value">£454.22</div>
            <div class="card-sub">Year to date</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">All Time Total</div>
            <div class="card-value">£2,308.20</div>
            <div class="card-sub">Since tracking</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">Best Month</div>
            <div class="card-value">£454.22</div>
            <div class="card-sub">Jan 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-label">2026 Avg/Month</div>
            <div class="card-value">£454.22</div>
            <div class="card-sub">Average</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MONTHLY BREAKDOWN -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Monthly Breakdown</div>
        <div class="placeholder-box">
            <p>📋 Monthly dividend income table</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 0;">This section will display your month-by-month dividend income across all years.</p>
            <code>Jan: £454.22 | Feb: £429.02 | Mar: £384.18 | Apr: £330.46...</code>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- YIELD TRACKING -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Portfolio Yield Analysis</div>
        <div class="cards-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-label">Blended Yield</div>
                <div class="card-value">9.83%</div>
                <div class="card-sub">Current weighted average</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-label">Total Portfolio</div>
                <div class="card-value">£44,953</div>
                <div class="card-sub">Invested</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="placeholder-box" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            <p>📈 Investment breakdown by yield category</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 0;">This section will show your portfolio allocation across different yield tiers (Low Risk, Medium Risk, High Risk, etc.)</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- YIELD TRENDS -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Yield Trends Over Time</div>
        <div class="placeholder-box">
            <p>📊 Historical yield trends chart</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 0;">This section will display how your blended yield has changed over the past months, helping you track yield management.</p>
            <code>Jan 2026: 9.83% | Dec 2025: 10.40% | Nov 2025: 10.17%...</code>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SETUP INSTRUCTIONS -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="empty-state">
            <div class="empty-state-icon">⚙️</div>
            <h2>Ready to Connect Your Data?</h2>
            <p>This is your personal Dividend Tracker. To display your monthly income data, yield analysis, and portfolio trends, connect your data source.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim);">Contact your administrator to set up data syncing from your portfolio management system.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
